                <note rend="inline" type="source">123 Lane, Clayton/118: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to Mr.
                            <persName type="to">William Phillips</persName>, Personal Representative
                        of President <persName>Roosevelt</persName> in India</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-04-26T21:00:00-04:00"
                            >April 26, 1943—9 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>216. Your 288, April 16, 2 p.m. Lane’s designation as Commercial Attaché
                    canceled.</p>
                <p>In lieu thereof, he is designated Secretary with the additional title of Director
                    of War Economic Operations.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
